	<h1>Logo</h1>
	{include file="/obj/byline.tpl"}
	<div class="headingbox">
		<h1><em>the</em> Story</h1>
		<div class="justify">
			<p>A small rose leaf picked up in 1984 inspired the founders of Life-Link to use it as <strong>the symbol</strong> for this global peace programme for youth and schools worldwide. The green leaf symbolises life in several ways; the green chlorophyll as a biologically fundamental catalyst, plants as necessary links between organic and inorganic life and flowers as an inspiration for art, poetry, and music.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
